                        <h1>About CEA</h1>                                  
                        The <A href="http://www.CE.org" target=_blank>Consumer Electronics Association (CEA)</A> unites 2,200 companies within the consumer technology industry. Members tap into valuable and innovative members-only resources: unparalleled market research, networking opportunities with business advocates and leaders, up-to-date educational programs and technical training, exposure in extensive promotional programs, and representation from the voice of the industry, CEA, promoting and advancing member needs and interests. <A href="http://www.ce.org/Membership/JoinCEA/default.aspx" target=_blank>Join the Consumer Electronics Association to strengthen your business' future.</A> <BR><BR><STRONG>Information</STRONG> <BR><A href="http://www.CE.org" target=_blank>CEA</A> is the industry authority on market research and forecasts; consumer surveys; legislative and regulatory news; engineering standards; training resources and more. <BR><BR><STRONG>Connections <BR></STRONG>Stay in touch with key industry leaders, government representatives, buyers, the media and others through <A href="http://www.CE.org" target=_blank>CEA</A> conferences, meetings and online forums. <BR><BR><STRONG>Exposure</STRONG> <BR><A href="http://www.CE.org" target=_blank>CEA</A> produces the International CES, the world's largest consumer technology tradeshow. It unites more than 130,000 retail buyers, distributors, manufacturers, market analysts, importers, exporters, and press from more than 140 countries. CEA members receive discounted floor space and other benefits when they <A href="/print/exhibitors/space/default.asp">exhibit at CES</A>. <BR><BR><STRONG>Influence</STRONG> <BR>There truly is strength in numbers. The association's united voice before Congress as well as federal and state agencies protects your company's business interests. <BR><BR><STRONG>Education</STRONG> <BR>CEA's research library, workshops and educational programs, technical training and certification programs are tools for member companies' success. <BR><BR><STRONG>Advantage</STRONG> <BR>Members using&nbsp;CEA's resources have a built-in lead in today's competitive marketplace. <BR><BR><STRONG>Mission Statement</STRONG><BR>CEA's mission is to grow the consumer electronics industry.<BR><BR>Not a member yet? <A href="http://www.ce.org/Membership/JoinCEA/default.aspx" target=_blank>Join CEA today. </A><BR>
    
